SideWays:

SideWays avoided the blas barely as his paint was peeling from the heat. "You 
guys walked into something better left to the big boys." His wrist closed 
reopening. "Try this you thundercracker wanna be." He fired a volley of 
magnetic pulses. "Lets see what you do when your bodies used as a conducter 
boy." He stopped picking up Rook and dived into the hole in the base. 
Crosswase still being the head whistled. "Heh, your right, we need to get 
farther indoors, that way fliers will have troubl.... what are you supposed 
to be?" He stopped stairing right at Pumpskin.
